You are building a gamified AI English Level Test for ENGZ using Next.js 15, TypeScript, Prisma, and OpenAI.

Requirements:
1. Pages:
   - /leveltest (intro with CTA)
   - /leveltest/quiz (vocab + grammar + writing sections)
   - /leveltest/result (locked -> unlocked after login)
2. Each question has a 10-second countdown timer; auto-skip when time is up.
3. Questions gradually increase in difficulty.
4. After completion:
   - Show blurred result with ‚ÄúLogin to view result‚Äù button.
   - Once logged in, fetch test data and show:
     - Scores (vocab, grammar, writing)
     - Avg speed, rank, score chart
     - AI-generated Korean feedback
     - Motivational English tagline (10 levels)
     - 4-week personalized routine
5. Add CTA for ‚ÄúStart Free 7-Day Trial‚Äù linked to Stripe checkout.
6. Design:
   - Orange/Ivory ENGZ theme
   - Rounded cards, progress bar, Framer Motion transitions
   - Korean-friendly text, English-only questions
7. Store test results in Prisma `LevelTest` model.

Goal:
Deliver a smooth, adaptive, gamified English level test experience with real-time countdowns, AI-generated personalized feedback, and Stripe-linked onboarding.
